{"tid":872103,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"高普話利物浦係狗！","createTime":"2018-10-22T12:37:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T15:16:07.000Z","uid":94771,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"25f02fcbd82b8844c645ed65a310d73e04e20b3e","tid":872103,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T12:37:23.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=24XembZovXu9sHLQTS2ZHDCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=b8b8aba1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】領隊高普居然將自己帶領的利物浦比喻作狗，為甚麼？<br />\n<br />\n利物浦今季的踢法不再是有前冇後的高位壓迫，而且變得沉穩，應守則守，上場鬥哈特斯菲爾德領先1:0後，未有繼續大舉施壓，反而注重防守，最終力保勝局，9場英超取得7勝2和，跟榜首曼城同分。<br />\n<br />\n高普（Jurgen Klopp）表示：「去年，我們最強之處是高位壓迫，但當對手不打算真正踢足球時，我們就麻煩了。<span style=\"color: red;\">就像一頭狗，若你不給牠最喜愛的玩具，給牠其他東西，牠就會想：我不要，我要另一個，我要踢高位壓迫。」</span><br />\n<br />\n這名四眼名帥入主紅軍後未嚐冠軍滋味，他坦言球隊正一步一步進步：「現在，我們要在中場有更好的壓迫。不過，對哈軍時我們的中場壓迫不是問題，問題是控球在腳的時候，可以做得更好。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c92cf4d26d2d47450e365885f55c948ef46e5e40","tid":872103,"uid":5649,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T12:38:42.000Z","msg":"利迷：高普係曼狗"},{"pid":"54068c5006ea360afc7c0ce65f76cd7a8b0646be","tid":872103,"uid":12000,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T12:55:23.000Z","msg":"高普死獌狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26ecd60ade4834bca171b010fe4ea9cd952d526f","tid":872103,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T13:58:07.000Z","msg":"冇講錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c7780937a1bccfd403b87e49b6396b6ee80c96a","tid":872103,"uid":4187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:35:22.000Z","msg":"四眼撚人高普<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79005c2874d8264ac62ff17f168afb